13
00:02:07,736 --> 00:02:09,172
[ENGINE REVVING]

14
00:02:09,216 --> 00:02:10,478
[SNIFFLES]

15
00:02:20,705 --> 00:02:22,272
[ENGINE REVVING]

16
00:02:31,586 --> 00:02:33,153
[ENGINE REVVING]

17
00:02:50,518 --> 00:02:52,911
[INHALING SHARPLY]

18
00:02:57,351 --> 00:03:00,528
