in the bottom of the quarry
down at St. Francisville.

175
00:14:46,015 --> 00:14:48,452
Police think he drove it
off the edge on purpose.

176
00:14:48,496 --> 00:14:50,324
Mm...

177
00:14:50,367 --> 00:14:51,978
No, Mom,
you must be mistaken. I...

178
00:14:53,153 --> 00:14:54,415
[CHUCKLES] That's...

179
00:14:55,503 --> 00:14:56,939
But they...

180
00:14:57,809 --> 00:15:00,116
