his cell phone back,

995
01:03:11,570 --> 01:03:13,615
and then abruptly
went back into the house.

996
01:03:13,659 --> 01:03:15,704
That's when Logan got spooked.

997
01:03:15,748 --> 01:03:18,185
He got a screwdriver
and held on to it in the car.

998
01:03:19,578 --> 01:03:21,101
And he says he fell asleep.

999
01:03:23,234 --> 01:03:24,844
-Asleep?
-Yeah.

1000
01:03:25,889 --> 01:03:27,673
Come on, man.

1001
01:03:27,716 --> 01:03:30,458
You're so convinced
he had nothing to do it,
you're not making sense.

1002
01:03:30,502 --> 01:03:36,029
Sometime after midnight,
Danny went upstairs with intent
to bludgeon Rachel to death.

1003
01:03:37,378 --> 01:03:39,206
Rachel was asleep at that time.

1004
01:03:41,034 --> 01:03:42,906
You may recall

1005
01:03:42,949 --> 01:03:45,865
a brownish lamp
in the living room
with a very heavy base?

1006
01:03:48,346 --> 01:03:51,218
Well, Danny
got a kitchen knife,

1007
01:03:51,262 --> 01:03:53,525
cut the cord
and used that lamp

1008
01:03:53,568 --> 01:03:55,092
as the primary weapon.

1009
01:03:56,745 --> 01:03:58,747
MITCH: And Rachel knew
this was happening?

1010
01:03:59,400 --> 01:04:01,402
Yeah. We think so.

1011
01:04:01,446 --> 01:04:03,665
Danny probably thought
that one blow to her head

1012
01:04:03,709 --> 01:04:05,537
would have been
sufficient to kill her,

1013
01:04:05,580 --> 01:04:08,975
like on TV. Well, it didn't.

1014
01:04:09,019 --> 01:04:10,934
-In fact, she fought back.
-[DANNY SCREAMS]

1015
01:04:12,326 --> 01:04:14,938
Danny then used
the kitchen knife to stab her.

1016
01:04:14,981 --> 01:04:16,374
[RACHEL CRIES]

1017
01:04:16,417 --> 01:04:19,638
But the kitchen knife
was only two inches long.

1018
01:04:19,681 --> 01:04:22,771
So at some point,
Danny grabbed a pair of scissors

1019
01:04:22,815 --> 01:04:24,773
from the sewing table,

1020
01:04:24,817 --> 01:04:26,210
and stabbed her with those.

1021
01:04:26,253 --> 01:04:28,125
[RACHEL SCREAMS]

1022
01:04:29,909 --> 01:04:31,780
Did she know it was Danny?

1023
01:04:31,824 --> 01:04:34,566
Well, the struggle
went on for several minutes,

1024
01:04:34,609 --> 01:04:36,568
and even though
we suppose the room was dark,

1025
01:04:36,611 --> 01:04:38,613
