recognized his voice.

1026
01:04:38,657 --> 01:04:41,399
And apparently,
there was a great deal
of shouting between them.

1027
01:04:41,442 --> 01:04:42,879
That's probably
what woke the children.

1028
01:04:45,403 --> 01:04:46,839
Rachel had, um,

1029
01:04:46,883 --> 01:04:49,450
marks on her arms
and what we presume to be

1030
01:04:49,494 --> 01:04:51,626
Danny's skin
under her fingernails.

1031
01:04:53,933 --> 01:04:55,935
I mean...

1032
01:04:55,979 --> 01:04:58,633
She was fighting
for her life, Mitch.

1033
01:04:58,677 --> 01:05:00,897
There's no doubt
she recognized the attacker.

1034
01:05:02,811 --> 01:05:05,858
My notes say that she suffered
from a severed
left carotid artery

1035
01:05:05,902 --> 01:05:08,208
which resulted
in exsanguination...

1036
01:05:08,252 --> 01:05:10,341
bleeding to death.

1037
01:05:10,384 --> 01:05:13,474
That would likely be
the official cause of death
when the report is completed.

1038
01:05:15,737 --> 01:05:18,305
Mitch, I've been doing this
for 20 years. I've never...

1039
01:05:19,959 --> 01:05:21,221
[SIGHS]

1040
01:05:21,265 --> 01:05:23,093
I've never seen
anything like this.

1041
01:05:23,136 --> 01:05:24,659
Lamp,

1042
01:05:24,703 --> 01:05:26,096
knife,

1043
01:05:26,139 --> 01:05:27,358
scissors.

1044
01:05:52,252 --> 01:05:55,125
[RACHEL'S VOICEMAIL
